NSFG: Initial Descriptives Emily Pollock 2019-08-09 Chapter 1 Preface This book contains the NSFG data descriptives for 2006-2015 as it relates to the sexual partnership patterns of 15-44 year olds. This is to get a sense of the dataset before conducting further analysis. What does the data look like, what is missing, etc. Unless otherwise specifed, NSFG survey weights are used.
